      "title": "EU concerned on use of PTA",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Delegation of the European Union in Sri Lanka says that it is concerned about reports on the use of the Prevention of Terrorism Act in recent arrests,",
        "The EU in Sri Lanka says it refers to the information given by the Government of Sri Lanka to the International Community about the de-facto moratorium of the use of the Prevention of Terrorism Act.",
        "SL Navy recovers prescription drugs worth Rs. 4.5 million in Mannar"
